{"tid":1917661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎迪士尼技工確診新冠肺炎樂園仍開放","createTime":"2020-03-09T15:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T15:12:46.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8f4d801c1af5cfb326749d83c35c0eb64a104d","tid":1917661,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎迪士尼樂園公布，一名維修技工周末時確診新型冠狀肺炎，惟強調技工不是和遊客接觸的第一線人員，因此樂園不會因此關閉。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼已調查曾和病患接觸的人，目前有三人隔離中。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼表示，會提供手部消毒液予入園遊客，並呼籲遊客排隊時要保持一定距離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2398563/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%92%E4%BB%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2398563%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%259C%2592%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c09826e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2398563/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%92%E4%BB%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/V0BYQVxPPpTdS/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FV0BYQVxPPpTdS%2Fsource.gif&h=4b3938b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bdd40e589f0c77f6e97c7eaa5a3da986a9c5f87","tid":1917661,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"洗手洗手洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}